<br>
My book configuration seems to work pretty well.  Makes it easy to find nearly everything.<br>
<br>
Attack - Just what it says.  DDs, DOTs, Dmg Shield<br>
<br>
Shield - All defenses with shield icon<br>
<br>
Div  - Anything which uses divination skill (has eyeball icon) like invis, see invis, serpent sight, etc.<br>
<br>
Mez/Charm - Best mezzes on left page, best charms on right.  Move obsolete spells back a page or two as you move up.  My stuns are 1 page back from this mark.<br>
<br>
Enchant - All enchantment spells<br>
<br>
Pet - All pet related spells<br>
<br>
Buffs - Leave extra pages for this one.  Haste, melee buffs on left page, mind buffs on right page.  Move obsolete spells back a page or two when leveling.<br>
<br>
Debuffs - Slows, Tashes, Cripples, etc.<br>
<br>
I leave the bottom two tabs open.  This is a carryover from my wizard... I use the "9" and "0" hotkeys for instant-cast items.  JBoots, etc.  Someday my epic will be here.  :)<br>
